comments[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-06-19T05:22:23.364Z",claude-code-agent,"Implemented pm context --fields (GH-156 follow-up to --depth full). Projects focus rows (high_level/low_level/blocked_fallback/recently_created/unparented) to a chosen field subset for low-token reads. New exported helpers parseContextFocusFields (validate+dedup) + projectContextFocusRows in context.ts; ContextResult.focus_fields echoes the projection; renderContextMarkdown renders projected key:value lines (drops recently-created date prefix). Works across markdown/TOON/JSON + pm_context MCP options.fields. Selectable: id,title,type,status,priority,order,deadline,assignee,tags,updated_at,parent,children_total,children_closed,completion_pct,created_at. Tests in context-command.spec.ts. Docs: COMMANDS.md 'Calendar and Context'."
